  "title": "Flexi / Locum Physiotherapist - Singaporean/PR only",
  "description": "<p>We are recruiting Locum Physiotherapist for various local healthcare institution in the intermediate and long-term care (ILTC) sector.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Roles and Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct initial assessments for new client admissions</li>\n  <li>Conduct 6-monthly Care Plan and program reviews</li>\n  <li>Conduct InterRai assessments as required (training will be provided if necessary)</li>\n  <li>Prescribe and execute individual and group therapy programs and activities.</li>\n  <li>Assist and engage residents with behaviors of concern</li>\n  <li>Review and revise therapy program schedules with proper documentation</li>\n  <li>Liaise closely with other healthcare professionals to encourage a holistic approach to care</li>\n  <li>Participate in multidisciplinary case discussions</li>\n  <li>Participate in continuing education, training, and research activities when opportunities arise</li>\n  <li>Support Active Rehabilitation under Community Rehabilitation if need arises.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree or Diploma in Physiotherapy</li>\n  <li>Full AHPC Registration</li>\n  <li>At least two years of experience working in a healthcare setting</li>\n  <li>Passionate about Physiotherapy</li>\n  <li>Good communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Fluency in local languages will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated to engage in continuous learning and education in the field of Physiotherapy</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>SG Rehab Recruitment Division</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Email: hr@sgrehab.com</li>\n  <li>Web: www.sgrehab.com</li>\n  <li>Company Registration No.: 201435598H | EA Licence No.: 17C8839</li>\n</ul>\n<p><em><strong>SG REHAB: Wherever you are, we take you further.</strong></em></p>\n<p>Should you be interested for this role, apply now and we will be in touch with you shortly to advance your application. Kindly note that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Types: Part-time, Contract, Temporary, Freelance</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Pay: $3,000.00 - $10,000.00 per month</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Flexible schedule</li>\n</ul>\n<p>License/Certification:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>AHPC registered (Required)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Work Location: In person</p>",
