    "description": "<p>SG Rehab is a headhunting and recruitment firm serving the local healthcare sphere. We specialize in the placement of Occupational Therapists, Physiotherapists and Speech Therapists in both full-time and locum positions with healthcare organizations across the whole spectrum of healthcare settings islandwide.</p>\n\n<p>We are in the line of people. And that is why we place people at the heart of all our processes. Between “Human” and “Resource”, we believe “Human” is more important. When we are Human about our processes, the Resource will care for itself.</p>\n",
